r.\nIn the other galaxies, the properties of the clusters are similar to those\nobserved in other, non-shell, elliptical galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Jun 2006 18:22:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Jun 2006 08:13:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
