, is large and positive, and\ncorrespondingly the value of |g1(0) / f1(0)| is reduced with respect to the one\nobtained with the conventional assumption g2(q**2) = 0 based on exact SU(3)\nsymmetry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Jun 2006 14:18:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Oct 2006 13:27:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
